composio

composio 0.1.24

USAGE

$ generate [(-o, --output-dir directory)] [--compact] [--transpiled] [--typ
e-tools] --toolkits text...

DESCRIPTION

Generate TypeScript types for toolkits, tools, and triggers from the Compos
io API.

Environment Variables:
  COMPOSIO_TOOLKIT_VERSION_<TOOLKIT>  Override toolkit version (e.g., COMPO
SIO_TOOLKIT_VERSION_GMAIL=20250901_00)
                                      Use "latest" or unset to use the late
st version.

OPTIONS

